line_1: Soft-swoln and pale, here lay the Hydropsy:
line_2: For ever fed with watery Supply;

line_1: Soft-swoln and pale, here lay the Hydropsy:
line_2: For still he drank, and yet he still was dry.

line_1: Soft-swoln and pale, here lay the Hydropsy:
line_2: Mother of Spleen, in Robes of various Dye,
